\id MIC - Michah 6:8 translated (Kathy Glasgow) and consultant checked (Paulus Kieviet) 2022
\h Micah
\toc1 Micah (heading in book)
\toc2 Micah
\toc3 Micah
\mt1 Mayka
\mt4 (Micah)
\c 6
\s1 Gun-guna Nipa Wangarr Jal A-nirra Nginyipa Barra Ny-yinda Barra Ny-yorkiya
\q1 
\v 8 Alay, ny-jurnarra ny-jaliyarra ny-yorkiya, nyi-gugaliya,
\q1 Wangarr gipa biy-gurdagurdarrana gun-nga gun-molamola.
\q1 Ya? Nipa jal a-nirra nginyipa barra ny-yinmiya barra ny-yorkiya?
\q2 Wurra nginyipa barra ny-yinda barra ny-yorkiya gun-molamola.
\q2 Jal nyi-ni barra ny-yorkiya ny-junggaja barra burrwa.
\q2 Delipa nyi-negiya barra ny-yorkiya,
\q3 Wangarr ny-jurdajurdamunga ny-jamburda. 
